metadata.name: The Virtual Blunt
metadata.description:
Decades ago, the legendary Virtual Joint was passed to millions of potheads around the world, via AIM, Hotmail, Yahoo Chat Rooms, various message boards, forums, and other electronic means. 

We must continue this tradition and keep the spirit alive.

Pass a Virtual Blunt to your friends, pass a Virtual Blunt to your enemies, burn a Virtual Blunt as a symbolic, web3 smoke sesh, burn a Virtual Blunt as a symbol of your sobriety, whatever you want. Get creative, do whatever you want with yours, but always, ALWAYS, pass it to the left ‚óÄÔ∏è
